Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我升入了二年級
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:54.84,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\blur1\3c&HE7BB9A&\c&H834131&}二年生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千她們...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離畢業還有二年 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 聚在一起的人比想像的要多不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且小朋和小悅也在一個班級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家那麼喜歡矢野嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就這樣分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該會有多寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 她叫黑沼爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫她貞子就可以了 多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那反應 還是毫無進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的們 去走廊排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開學典禮要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍 今年也多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夢見和她交往了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 明彥的Live帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面的 站的緊湊點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千笠好像是在C班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真沒想到大家都在同一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼矢野那麼拽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你沒送給他巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是都準備好了嗎 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節那天 絕對發生什麼事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天以後兩個人就一直不太自然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 也說明了爽子認真地意識到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春假啊 週末什麼的 明明有那麼多機會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛就是時機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就被甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}風早好像不收本命巧克力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直 一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是說 風早不打算和任何人交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經有其他喜歡的女孩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃希望他做「大家的風早」的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎終於能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就沒有一點僥倖的想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和他在同一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到他對我說「早上好」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也已經是像做夢一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻無法忘記兩人在一起的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還期待著更多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是太貪心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別有用心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明彥的決勝台詞太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想讓大家也聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貞子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您認識我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐我旁邊啊 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫三浦健人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種人真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這不是有眉毛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 表情好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 女孩子不可以皺眉頭的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 快點把班委定下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先由班長開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我來決定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 選 誰 好 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是石化的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險 差點就剝奪了別人的樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 健人要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很顯眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不會比我更顯眼的 放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子隔壁那傢伙好特別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新物種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推薦黑沼同學做生活委員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼同學很擅長照顧花草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧花壇的工作 一直都是爽子在做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也會笑不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果很辛苦的話 我也會來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個 風紀委員是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城治 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立 敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那裡也...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長工作的心得和對老師應有的崇敬之情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好詳細跟你說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叫你不要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是麻煩才好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是滿腦子樂觀的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說我也不會等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去圖書室了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}那個超有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼 要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要多留一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給花壇播種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開學式還要去社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 已經定好日子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹的結婚典禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 快了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會去問大叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 快要比賽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春季的預選賽 不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了的話就晉級？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要到夏天 春季的比賽是用來熱身的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 贏下就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今晚我會去吃拉麵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事情 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啥事 就是換班的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了嗎 當時那麼有誠意的去拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(548,188)\bord1\frz7.933\fad(300,0)}爽\N子\N可\N以\N給\N你\N除\N靈
